   "source": [
    "## Step 4 вЂ” Test Case Generator (Stage 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "A **4-agent pipeline** generates test cases from the ParsedSpec:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Planner** вЂ” reads `test_gen_config.yaml`, decides pyramid split and test levels\n",
    "- **Generator** вЂ” creates test cases per AC covering positive, negative and edge scenarios\n",
    "- **Critic** вЂ” automatically identifies coverage gaps and flags missing scenarios\n",
    "- **Refiner** вЂ” finalises, deduplicates and locks the TestSpec\n",
    "\n",
    "In **live mode** each agent calls Mistral 7B via Ollama. In **simulated mode** the\n",
    "agents run the same logic locally without LLM calls вЂ” demonstrating the full\n",
    "agentic loop structure.\n",
    "\n",
    "Produces **24 test cases** across 3 layers вЂ” API, UI and E2E.\n"
   ]
  },
