    "## Step 7 вЂ” Code Synthesis Module (Stage 5)\n",
    "\n",
    "Jinja2 templates render each test case into real executable code.\n",
    "\n",
    "- **No LLM is involved at this stage** вЂ” output is 100% deterministic\n",
    "- Each template is framework-specific and swappable via config\n",
    "- Output is written directly to `/generated/` and ready to run\n",
    "- Three files produced: Java API tests В· TypeScript UI tests В· TypeScript E2E tests"
   ]
  },
